DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to compare the serum levels of estradiol, progesterone, FSH and LH in NPC-01 or IKH-01 one treatment cycle with those in before and after administration cycle.
DOC.brief_title: Pharmacodynamics of NPC-01/IKH-01; Effect of NPC-01/IKH-01 on Sexual Hormone Concentrations in Healthy Female Volunteers
DOC.mesh_term: Norethindrone acetate, ethinyl estradiol, ferrous fumarate drug combination
DOC.criteria: Healthy female aged between 20 to 35 years BMI:18.026.0 Females who are pregnant Drug use affecting sex hormone secretion
